data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. NEED SPACE? Welcome to this fantastic home in beautiful Spring Hill, Florida situated on a 1/2 acre lot with NO HOA!!! This home boasts 2,269 sq ft of living space with 3 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, perfect for a growing family or those who love to entertain. As you enter, you're greeted with a SPLIT FLOOR PLAN that offers privacy and convenience. The highlight of the family room is a beautiful WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE, perfect for cozy evenings with loved ones. Step outside to the screened-in lanai, complete with a rear covered porch featuring a unique metal ceiling that gives off a Key West tropical vibe. The SALTWATER POOL is perfect for cooling off on hot summer days and the outdoor kitchen area is a great spot for hosting barbecues and pool parties. The entire home features vinyl plank flooring throughout, giving it a modern and sleek look. NO CARPET means easy maintenance and allergy-friendly living. The exterior of the home was recently painted in 2020, giving it a fresh and updated look. The POOL PUMP REPLACED IN 2023, ensuring optimal performance. The POOL WAS RESURFACED IN 2018, providing a pristine and inviting swimming experience. One of the unique features of this property is the separate full bathroom off the pool area. It is complete with a walk-in shower and features floating wood slat flooring for slip resistance and a sauna-like feel. The master suite boasts HIS AND HERS walk-in closets, offering ample storage space. The spacious master bathroom features dual sinks, an incredible JETTED JACUZZI TUB, and a separate walk-in shower. Throughout the home, you'll notice beautiful WOOD BEAMS in the family room and master bedroom, adding character and charm. Modern ceiling fans provide comfort and style in every room. The hall bathroom services the two additional bedrooms and features dual sinks and a tub/shower combo, making it convenient for daily use. This home is equipped with a TANKLESS WATER HEATER with a built-in water softener, ensuring a constant supply of hot water. The toilets have been updated for efficiency and style. Newer sliding glass doors lead to the pool area, allowing for easy access and seamless indoor-outdoor living. The side gate provides easy access to the spacious backyard, perfect for storing an RV or boat. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring updated STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, a tiled backsplash, and industrial-style shelving. The CUSTOM POT FILLER adds convenience and style to this modern kitchen. Don't miss your opportunity to view this home!
